          &nbsp;||<br>
          _||__/|&nbsp;</div><br>
        <div class=3D"droptext">Each character is designed to be clearly di=
stinguishable from similar looking characters.
          While this seems obvious, it comes with costs, like inferior long=
=E2=80=93text readability and a less consistent
          appearance. I tried to reach this goal with minimal tradeoffs.
        </div>
